"Unit Arrays — | Operator

"| scalar conversion
L = 6m
L|cm
L|mm

"| vector conversion per element
v = [5m; 3m; 0.02rad]
v|[cm; mm; rad]

"Matrix with units
E = 200000MPa
A = 100cm^2
L_b = 3m
k_a = E*A/L_b
K = k_a*[1; -1 | -1; 1]
K|[kN/m; kN/m | kN/m; kN/m]

"Simple solve without units
K_n = [4; -2 | -2; 4]
F_n = [10; 0]
u_n = lsolve(K_n; F_n)
